			<div class="content" id="post-content-3972209">
									

<p>Round 2 of the OCT: Agent Johnson vs. Wobbles the shark. <sub>I'm just messin around here you know I love you guys</sub></p>
<p>Thanks to <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/othellothecat" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3213383); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3213383&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1537237648" alt="OthellotheCat" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3213383)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/othellothecat" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3213383); return false;">OthellotheCat</a></span> (&quot;So many people are going to hate this. Or at least, hate Johnson.&quot;) and <span class="printuser avatarhover"><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3440103); return false;"><img class="small" src="http://www.wikidot.com/avatar.php?userid=3440103&amp;amp;size=small&amp;amp;timestamp=1537237648" alt="Captain Kirby" style="background-image:url(http://www.wikidot.com/userkarma.php?u=3440103)" /></a><a href="http://www.wikidot.com/user:info/captain-kirby" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.listeners.userInfo(3440103); return false;">Captain Kirby</a></span> (&quot;How dare? I'd upvote, but how dare?&quot;) for feedback in chat.</p>
<p>Picture credits:<br />
Strip mall CC on flickr <a href="https://www.flickr.com/photos/dt10111/2975388487">here</a><br />
Cabin courtesy of wikimedia commons <a href="https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Giant_Forest_Cabin_A.jpg">here</a><br />
Van CC <a href="http://www.geograph.org.uk/photo/4523306">here</a>, edited by me</p>
<p>I hope your week is going well. Thanks for reading this.</p>

