														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-3972317">
									

<p>I think this is the second OCT tale I've read where &quot;fun&quot; and grim canons meet and&#8230; it just doesn't work out.</p>
<p>This is well-written and probably the natural conclusion of such a meeting, and has some details I really like (the nasty portrayal of mnestics was cool), but&#8230; it's deeply unpleasant, without the contest wouldn't exist, and doesn't really give a reason for itself beyond that.</p>
<p>-1</p>

